{
  "text": "where we have taken (1, 2) to be incoming and [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] to be outgoing. We work in split signature so that we can treat z andz as independent real variables. The OPE limit, we are interested in, is z 3 \u2192 z 4 withz 34 held fixed. The corresponding Mellin amplitude is given by,",
